Families of distributions

The dpqr functions of available bounded distributions.

dashw() pashw() qashw() rashw()
The arcsecant hyperbolic Weibull distribution
djohnsonsb() pjohnsonsb() qjohnsonsb() rjohnsonsb()
The Johnson SB distribution
dkum() pkum() qkum() rkum()
The Kumaraswamy distribution
dleeg() pleeg() qleeg() rleeg()
The Log-extended exponential-geometric distribution
dubs() pubs() qubs() rubs()
The unit-Birnbaum-Saunders distribution
duburrxii() puburrxii() quburrxii() ruburrxii()
The unit-Burr-XII distribution
duchen() puchen() quchen() ruchen()
The unit-Chen distribution
dughne() pughne() qughne() rughne()
The unit-Half-Normal-E distribution
dughnx() pughnx() qughnx() rughnx()
The unit-Half-Normal-X distribution
dugompertz() pugompertz() qugompertz() rugompertz()
The unit-Gompertz distribution
dugumbel() pugumbel() qugumbel() rugumbel()
The unit-Gumbel distribution
dulogistic() pulogistic() qulogistic() rulogistic()
The unit-Logistic distribution
duweibull() puweibull() quweibull() ruweibull()
The unit-Weibull distribution
